OL,5,BUsing the teletext editor              
OL,7,BThe zxnet editor has a built in help   
OL,8,Bfacility which can be accessed via the 
OL,9,EHelpBlink in the top right-hand corner.
OL,11,BThe built-in help describes the process
OL,12,Bof entering teletextEcontrol codesBto  
OL,13,Echange colourBetc. along with the more 
OL,14,Badvanced editing features.             
OL,16,BTeletext art is created by the addition
OL,17,BofEmosaic colourBcontrol codes, which  
OL,18,Bturn the character cells following it  
OL,19,Binto mosaicE"sixels"Blike this:W123456 
OL,20,E``````````````````````````````````2/3``
OL,21,B  Tweet your creations with _teletext  
OL,22,D]MGor join our discord.gg/JfytfS3xmg   
